                    <desc xml:id="abstract-en-309" xml:lang="en">A village of Beth Garmai.</desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="syr-Syrj">
                        <quote source="#bib309-2">ܩܪܝܬܳܐ ܕܚܰܪܝܒܐ ܒܰܐܬܪܐ ܕܒܶܝܬ ܓܰܪ̈ܡܰܝ ܕܒܐܽܘܚܕܳܢܐ ܕܟܰܪܟܽܘܟ ܒܥܪܐܩ.</quote>
                    </desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="ar">
                        <quote source="#bib309-3">قرية مندثرة في ولاية باجرمي التي  هي لواء كركوك في العراق</quote>
                    </desc>
                    <desc xml:lang="en">
                        <quote source="#bib309-4">an ancient village in the province of Bajermi (Beth Garmai), which is the Liwa of Kirkuk (in Iraq).</quote>
                    </desc>
